Account Id.description: The unique identifier for the account to which the ad group belongs.

Ad Group.description: The name or identifier of the ad group.

Campaign.description: The campaign to which the ad group is associated.

Client Id.description: The client identifier associated with the ad group.

Id.description: The unique identifier of the ad group label.

Parent Id.description: The identifier of the parent entity, if applicable.

Modified Time.description: The date and time when the ad group label was last modified.

Status.description: The status of the ad group label.
